title: Magic World Online CB Client (Ver. 0.91)
description:
Magic World Online? Closed Beta Starts on March 9

Magic World Online is a brand new free to play MMORPG published by Ingle Games.
This client is made for fist stage closed beta test. Closed beta accounts is still open for application now. You can visit their forum mwobbs.enjoymmo.com and try to get one.

Game Features
In Game Video Chat
Have you ever thought about communicating with your in-game teammates face to face? 

House System
Want to own a multifunctional house that&#039;ll meet your ever changing needs? 

In Game Robot and Auto Navigation
Getting fed up with the tiring and unnecessary mouse clicking in MMORPG? Spending hundreds of minutes to walk in a map and hoping something like the GPS auto navigation system could be your savior? 

Massive State War

Guild Castle and Moving Castle

Multiple Class Transfer

Visit official website http://mwo.enjoymmo.com for more details.
